Package voicesplitting.parsing

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    NoteEventParser
    A NoteEventParser is any class which can handle MIDI Note On and Note Off events.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EventParser
    An EventParser handles the interfacing between this program and MIDI files.
    MidiWriter
    A MidiWriter is able to take in MidiNotes and a TimeTracker, and write them out to a valid Midi File.
    NoteListGenerator
    A NoteListGenerator parses Note On and Note Off events and generates a List of the MidiNotes present in any given song.
